11  

Zedekia ne jahigni piero ariyo gabich kane odoko ruoth, morito piny kuom higni apar gachiel kodak Jerusalem. 
12  Timbene ne richo e nyim Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasache. Notamore winjo weche Jeremia jadolo, mane Ruoth Nyasaye ooro ire. 
13  

Bende ruoth Nebukadnezar nosemiyo okuong’ore e nying Nyasaye ni nobed e bwo lochne, to kata kamano nopiem kode, motamore duogo kuom Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel. 
14  Jodolo madongo duto bende kaachiel gi ji, noweyo Ruoth Nyasaye chuth, ka giluwo timbe makuero mag jopinje mamoko. Ne gidwanyo Od Ruoth Nyasaye, mane oseguedho mondo obed mare e Jerusalem.


15  Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasach kweregi notimo kinda kooronigi jootene pile nikech nokecho joge, kendo nohero kar dakne. 
16  To ne gimedo charo joote Nyasaye, ka gichayo wachne, kendo ginyiero jonabi mage, nyaka Ruoth Nyasaye nokecho kodgi, ma koro ne ok ginyal konyo.

